{"tid":1419890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲時你做緊咩？佢選擇左行出黎！","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:51:10.000Z","uid":53377,"like":191,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"563c8ea5ad036325baead08af4d7bcd3bef44fa0","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"借朋友acc出文<br />\n<br />\n我發個個夢係咁既，係岩岩個星期日銅鑼灣轉場去觀塘既狗鐵上，係我同我班fd面前出現左佢...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pdug5DD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdug5DD.png&h=a41765ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗得12-13歲 好瘦削 只有簡單裝備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋個刻真係好驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到佢自己一個人上車，應該無同齡朋友組隊，或者佢同朋友係轉場時失散咗<br />\n<br />\n見到咁既情況，我同班fd做到既只有俾我地個日收到既coupon俾佢，佢無出聲默默咁收到入褲袋 <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢睇唔睇到依個post、又唔知佢叫咩名，但記得用啲coupon買多啲野食<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好被補呀...你大把前途 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ff7016a9f9b31a48ec9058a3f8db5bf575e01b9c","tid":1419890,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:58:41.000Z","msg":"被捕"},{"pid":"966aa0102b58f99c06e224b6ebd96a3b5e99a174","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984dadfa4ea625f481281d0e47d831d82111fae3","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:05:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i