":"2019-08-06T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"我唔交稅住...<br />\n<br />\n唔交稅點可能?遲交都要加多5%。<br />\n<br />\n但你嘅評稅1日未完成,政府都唔可以開張稅單嚟收稅。<br />\n<br />\n打電話通知收唔到報稅單。拖一拖。<br />\n<br />\n張報稅表未簽名佢都唔可以開始。<br />\n<br />\n一於拖得就拖。吹呀!"},{"pid":"9406d9fa041795ef34647785734a037edf028090","tid":1419890,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aecb7ef17ba04056584fd5b9c365da7f9f3cc7a","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"305b440cc4b165b2520a943f5ce7dd46ef15c088","tid":1419890,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"未夠18歲有無案底㗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"如果真係被捕而被定罪 可能會警司警誡同時消除案底<br />\n<br />\n但必定對佢本人留下陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ccf14c4274e97a0a99586cf25f579e5b84fcdc","tid":1419890,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌 好心痛"},{"pid":"d9a9aea6163ddf0d7155f5a0d882defd4e3ace2a","tid":1419890,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5f0558154848c5dbea1c53734f6b26b5e489d1","tid":1419890,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aecb7ef17ba04056584fd5b9c365da7f9f3cc7a","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"305b440cc4b165b2