已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1647a7b0a0444a4db18ceb4b32d0130dd38ae57","tid":1419890,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"563c8ea5ad036325baead08af4d7bcd3bef44fa0","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"借朋友acc出文<br />\n<br />\n我發個個夢係咁既，係岩岩個星期日銅鑼灣轉場去觀塘既狗鐵上，係我同我班fd面前出現左佢...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pdug5DD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdug5DD.png&h=a41765ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗得12-13歲 好瘦削 只有簡單裝備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋個刻真係好驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到佢自己一個人上車，應該無同齡朋友組隊，或者佢同朋友係轉場時失散咗<br />\n<br />\n見到咁既情況，我同班fd做到既只有俾我地個日收到既coupon俾佢，佢無出聲默默咁收到入褲袋 <br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢睇唔睇到依個post、又唔知佢叫咩名，但記得用啲coupon買多啲野食<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好被補呀...你大把前途 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"好慚愧 覺得自己好對佢唔住<br />\n如果我早10年就企出黎 <br />\n佢一定唔洗咁細個就著哂裝備出黎行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4e134720405834c61c6ef56c19fb6edfa41b6f","tid":1419890,"uid":53377,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvK5e1J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvK5e1J.png&h=5fc29a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好細個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla